2014年國際足協世界盃是[[國際足協世界盃|世界盃]]史上成本最高的赛事<ref name=cc5739>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/news/story/_/id/1830732/2014-world-cup-set-most-lucrative-ever?cc=5739|title=World Cup set to be most lucrative ever|date=23 May 2014|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140531182956/http://www.espnfc.com/news/story/_/id/1830732/2014-world-cup-set-most-lucrative-ever?cc=5739|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比赛前夕巴西政府投入了140亿美元，大部分用于场馆建设和基建项目<ref name=cc5739/>。[[国际足联|国际足联]]在赛事决赛圈阶段亦花费近40亿<ref name="FIFA investment">{{cite web|title=Record World Cup numbers game for FIFA, Brazil|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/money/business/2014/05/22/record-world-cup-numbers-game-for-fifa-and-brazil/9458457/|publisher=USA Today|date=22 May 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620134155/http://www.usatoday.com/story/money/business/2014/05/22/record-world-cup-numbers-game-for-Fifa-and-brazil/9458457/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 场馆建设 ==
{{main|2014年世界杯足球赛比赛场馆}}
最终用在场馆建设的36亿美元比组织者先前预计的11亿美元<ref name="Inspection report">{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/mm/document/affederation/mission/fwc2014%5fbrazil%5fbid%5finspection%5freport%5fen%5f24491.pdf |title=FIFA's Inspection Report |format=PDF |accessdate=9 October 2011 |archive-date=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708194341/http://www.fifa.com/mm/document/affederation/mission/fwc2014%5fbrazil%5fbid%5finspection%5freport%5fen%5f24491.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>大大增多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2014-05-22/corruption-to-blame-for-some-brazil-world-cup-cost-rises|title=Corruption to blame for some Brazil World Cup cost rises|publisher=Bloomberg|date=23 May 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618204454/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2014-05-22/corruption-to-blame-for-some-brazil-world-cup-cost-rises|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/03/soccer-world-brazil-idUSL2E8F2GG820120403|title=Brazil World Cup stadiums on track, but costs soar|publisher=Reuters|date=3 April 2012|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709132942/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/03/soccer-world-brazil-idUSL2E8F2GG820120403|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有五座举办城市专门为世界杯新建场地，而首都[[巴西利亚|巴西利亚]]的[[巴西利亚国家体育场|巴西利亚国家体育场]]更是被拆毁重建，其与六座场地被全面翻新<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24897388|title=2014 Fifa World Cup: Where are the 12 host stadiums in Brazil?|publisher=BBC|date=3 December 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117054733/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24897388|dead-url=no}}</ref>。位于[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]的[[马拉卡纳体育场|马拉卡纳体育场]]是世界最大型的体育馆，曾享有世界杯决赛观众人数记录（199854），本届世界杯决赛将在此上演。[[巴西足球协会|巴西足球协会]]原本打算在[[莫伦比体育场|莫伦比体育场]]举办揭幕战，但由于场馆改善没有财务担保，而被2010年被搁置并由[[圣保罗体育场|圣保罗体育场]]取代<ref>{{cite web |url=http://theworldgame.sbs.com.au/2014-world-cup/news/1008887/Sao-Paulo-dropped-for-2014 |publisher=SBS |title=Sao Paulo dropped for 2014 |date=17 June 2010 |accessdate=17 June 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100628014015/http://theworldgame.sbs.com.au/2014-world-cup/news/1008887/Sao-Paulo-dropped-for-2014 |archivedate=2010年6月28日 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>。

首座全新体育场[[卡斯特劳体育场|卡斯特劳体育场]]2013年1月开始运作<ref name="NewVision">{{cite web|url=http://www.newvision.co.ug/news/639296-brazil-s-first-2014-world-cup-stadium-holds-matches.html|title=Brazil's first 2014 World Cup stadium holds matches|publisher=NewVision|date=28 January 2013|accessdate=30 January 2013|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226035833/http://www.newvision.co.ug/news/639296-brazil-s-first-2014-world-cup-stadium-holds-matches.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。六座场馆在[[2013年联合会杯|2013年联合会杯]]中使用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/confederationscup/destination/stadiums/index.html|title=Destination: Stadiums|publisher=FIFA|date=15 June 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2015-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719041548/http://www.fifa.com/confederationscup/destination/stadiums/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他六座错过了国际足联原定于2013年12月31日的竣工最后期限<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-25226088|title=Brazil World Cup: Six stadiums to miss Fifa deadline|publisher=BBC|date=5 December 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204053015/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-25226088|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年11月，圣保罗体育场的一次致命性的起重机倒塌事故，导致体育场部分遭损，两名工人遇害，给竣工带来阻碍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-25127897|title=Two die in Brazil World Cup stadium accident|publisher=BBC|date=27 November 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2018-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180411093057/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-25127897|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[库里奇巴|库里奇巴]][[拜沙达体育场|拜沙达体育场]]工期建站缓慢，让国际足联在2014年1月扬言放弃该场地作为主要场馆，除非在接下来的一个月取得实质性进展<ref name="Valcke ultimatum">{{cite web|title=World Cup venue in southern Brazil in danger of not being ready; FIFA's Valcke gives ultimatum|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/01/21/world-cup-venue-in-southern-brazil-in-danger-not-being-ready-fifa-valcke-gives/|publisher=Fox News Channel|accessdate=22 January 2014|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701174858/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/01/21/world-cup-venue-in-southern-brazil-in-danger-not-being-ready-fifa-valcke-gives/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。对进展感到满足后，国际足联证实库里提巴仍为主办城市<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/284527.html |title=Curitiba to stay as World Cup venue in Brazil |publisher=ESPN.co.uk |date=18 February 2014 |accessdate=2014-07-04 |archive-date=2015-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226040127/http://www.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/284527.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年头三个月，[[马瑙斯|马瑙斯]][[亚马逊体育场|亚马逊体育场]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://acritica.uol.com.br/craque/Manaus-Amazonas-Amazonia-Remo-Nacional-inauguracao-Arena-Amazonia_0_1098490157.html |title=Nacional empata com o Remo e é eliminado da Copa Verde |date=9 March 2014 |language=pt |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724141039/http://acritica.uol.com.br/craque/Manaus-Amazonas-Amazonia-Remo-Nacional-inauguracao-Arena-Amazonia_0_1098490157.html |archivedate=2014年7月24日 |accessdate=2014年7月4日 }}</ref>、[[纳塔尔_(巴西)|纳塔尔]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/rn/noticia/2014/01/arena-das-dunas-e-inaugurada-com-festa-e-vitoria-do-america-rn.html |title=Arena das Dunas é inaugurada com festa e vitórias de América-RN e ABC |date=26 January 2014 |language=pt |accessdate=2014-07-04 |archive-date=2017-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116184813/http://globoesporte.globo.com/rn/noticia/2014/01/arena-das-dunas-e-inaugurada-com-festa-e-vitoria-do-america-rn.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[阿雷格里港|阿雷格里港]]的场馆迎来首场测试赛<ref>{{cite web |url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/rs/futebol/campeonato-gaucho/noticia/2014/02/o-gigante-voltou-apos-mais-de-1-ano-inter-volta-ao-beira-rio-e-goleia-caxias.html |title=O Gigante voltou: após mais de 1 ano, Inter revê Beira-Rio e goleia o Caxias |date=15 February 2014 |language=pt |accessdate=2014-07-04 |archive-date=2017-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116184729/http://globoesporte.globo.com/rs/futebol/campeonato-gaucho/noticia/2014/02/o-gigante-voltou-apos-mais-de-1-ano-inter-volta-ao-beira-rio-e-goleia-caxias.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年5月，国际足联秘书长视察上述场馆时，对其准备工作表示担忧，要求额外的测试活动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://msn.foxsports.com/soccer/story/three-world-cup-stadiums-worry-fifa-after-inspection-052914|title=After final inspection, 3 Brazil World Cup stadiums worry FIFA|publisher=Fox Sports|date=29 May 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140531233955/http://msn.foxsports.com/soccer/story/three-world-cup-stadiums-worry-fifa-after-inspection-052914|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴西副体育部长路易斯·费尔南德斯则回应“没有可担心的”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.copa2014.gov.br/en/noticia/transcript-conference-call-brazil-deputy-minister-sport-luis-fernandes|title=Transcript of conference call - Brazil Deputy Minister of Sport Luis Fernandes|publisher=copa2014|date=29 May 2014|access-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140603125451/http://www.copa2014.gov.br/en/noticia/transcript-conference-call-brazil-deputy-minister-sport-luis-fernandes|archive-date=2014-06-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 基建项目 ==
2010年1月，巴西联邦政府估计举办世界杯赛事预计花费110亿美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-07/swiss-re-says-brazil-spending-for-world-cup-olympics-means-more-revenue.html|title=Swiss Re Says Brazil Spending for World Cup, Olympics Means More Revenue|date=8 April 2010|publisher=Bloomberg L.P.|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628093328/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-07/swiss-re-says-brazil-spending-for-world-cup-olympics-means-more-revenue.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并宣布为2014年世界杯比赛场馆的修葺减税，对主办城市<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.copa2014.org.br/en/news/3028/BRAZIL+SHALL+GRANT+TAX+BREAKS+FOR+2014+STADIUMS.html |title=Brazil shall grant tax breaks for 2014 stadiums |date=18 May 2010 |accessdate=30 October 2007 |publisher=Portal 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100526040010/http://www.copa2014.org.br/en/news/3028/BRAZIL+SHALL+GRANT+TAX+BREAKS+FOR+2014+STADIUMS.html |archivedate=2010年5月26日 }}</ref>和[[国际足联|国际足联]]在巴西的开支免征增值税<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10091277|title=World Cup: To tax or not to tax?|publisher=BBC News|date=11 May 2010|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2017-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127192206/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10091277|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

政府拨款18亿欧元用于2014年世界杯的工程建设<ref name="Brazil-Arab News Agency">{{cite web|url=http://www2.anba.com.br/noticia_esportes.kmf?cod=8705153|title=FIFA World Cup 2014 host cities to receive US$ 1.5 billion|date=22 July 2009|publisher=Brazil-Arab News Agency|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701222758/http://www2.anba.com.br/noticia_esportes.kmf?cod=8705153|archivedate=2014年7月1日|df=|accessdate=2014年7月4日}}</ref>。

本届赛事组委会视巴西机场为“大难题”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conmebol.com/en/content/airports-headache-2014-world-cup|title=Airports: the headache of the 2014 World Cup|publisher=CONMEBOL.com|date=15 April 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2017-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705133838/http://www.conmebol.com/en/content/airports-headache-2014-world-cup|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比赛期间估计60万人共300万人次搭乘飞机<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com.au/football/world-cup/poor-travel-options-to-test-600000-foreign-fans-who-flock-to-brazil-for-world-cup/story-fn9iws45-1226774265844|title=Poor travel options to test 600,000 foreign fans who flock to Brazil for World Cup|publisher=Fox Sports|date=3 December 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2016-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318064303/http://www.foxsports.com.au/football/world-cup/poor-travel-options-to-test-600000-foreign-fans-who-flock-to-brazil-for-world-cup/story-fn9iws45-1226774265844|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

国家立法确保加快国营机场建设工程<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.v-brazil.com/world-cup/2014/law-bureaucracy-airport-building-easier/ |title=Law reduces bureaucracy of airports building |publisher=v-brazil.com |date=8 June 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816220332/http://www.v-brazil.com/world-cup/2014/law-bureaucracy-airport-building-easier/ |archivedate=2014-08-16 |accessdate=2014-07-04 }}</ref>。然而，巴西政府2011年的研究，表明10-13号航站楼升级工程的完工赶不上比赛<ref name="Airports">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-13090122|title=Brazil's airports 'not ready for World Cup 2014'|publisher=BBC|date=15 April 2011|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2017-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171126202904/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-13090122|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴西总统[[迪尔玛·罗塞夫|迪尔玛·罗塞夫]]表示政府将强势介入，确保机场完工，开放民间投资。三大机场的运营权于2013年拍卖给私人机构<ref name="Airports"/>，费用估计108亿美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-19/airport-auction-tests-readiness-for-world-cup-corporate-brazil.html|title=Airport auction tests readiness for World Cup: Corporate Brazil|publisher=Bloomberg|date=19 November 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628215148/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-19/airport-auction-tests-readiness-for-world-cup-corporate-brazil.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

其他重大基础设施项目，相继在全国各地的铁道系统、[[轻轨|轻轨]]和快速公交线路展开，届时机场将连接市中心和比赛场馆，总里程预计超过4300公里<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ey.com/Publication/vwLUAssets/Sustainable_Brazil_-_World_Cup/$FILE/copa_2014.pdf|title=Sustainable Brazil: Social & Economic Impacts of the 2014 World Cup|publisher=Ernst & Young|page=13|year=2011|format=PDF|access-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140804202244/http://www.ey.com/Publication/vwLUAssets/Sustainable_Brazil_-_World_Cup/$FILE/copa_2014.pdf|archive-date=2014-08-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

为迎接大量旅客，巴西开发银行向全国酒店网络的建设拨款20亿亚雷尔<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.copa2014.gov.br/en/noticia/brazilian-development-bank-extends-financing-programme-hotel-sector|title=Brazilian Development Bank extends financing programme for the hotel sector|date=28 September 2012|publisher=copa2014|access-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140531201717/http://www.copa2014.gov.br/en/noticia/brazilian-development-bank-extends-financing-programme-hotel-sector|archive-date=2014-05-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]，这项开发也将用于即将举办的[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/money/2013/11/22/422-hotels-to-be-built-in-brazil-ahead-2016-olympics/|title=422 Hotels to be built in Brazil ahead of 2016 Olympics|publisher=Fox News Channel|date=22 November 2013|access-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308063602/http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/money/2013/11/22/422-hotels-to-be-built-in-brazil-ahead-2016-olympics/|archive-date=2014-03-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

许多工程计划被取消，如[[玛瑙斯|玛瑙斯]]和[[圣保罗|圣保罗]]的新[[单轨铁路|单轨铁路]]系统、[[贝洛奥里藏特|贝洛奥里藏特]]的地铁系统，其他项目预计不能赶在比赛前完工<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-27/failed-world-cup-projects-producing-rally-for-marcopolo.html|title=Failed World Cup projects producing rally for Marcopolo|date=27 March 2013|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140531183551/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-27/failed-world-cup-projects-producing-rally-for-marcopolo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.journalgazette.net/article/20140317/NEWS04/303179996|title=Brazil’s World Cup a broken promise|date=17 March 2014|publisher=Journal Gazette|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2017-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116190043/http://www.journalgazette.net/article/20140317/NEWS04/303179996|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.portal2014.org.br/andamento-obras/29/VLT+linha+1trecho+1+AeroportoTerminal+Asa+Sul.html |title=VLT linha 1-trecho 1 (Aeroporto/Terminal Asa Sul) |accessdate=5 October 2012 |language=pt |archive-date=2012-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120613204006/http://www.portal2014.org.br/andamento-obras/29/VLT+linha+1trecho+1+AeroportoTerminal+Asa+Sul.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.portal2014.org.br/andamento-obras/38/Cuiaba++VLT+CuiabaVarzea+Grande.html |title=VLT Cuiabá/Várzea Grande |accessdate=5 October 2012 |language=pt |archive-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231025733/http://www.portal2014.org.br/andamento-obras/38/Cuiaba++VLT+CuiabaVarzea+Grande.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2014年5月有报告指出，计划中的93个重大项目仅有36个完工<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/05/21/brazil-worldcup-economy-idUSL1N0O10CS20140521|title=World Cup protests threaten Brazil's economy and its image|date=21 May 2014|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140531183810/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/05/21/brazil-worldcup-economy-idUSL1N0O10CS20140521|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国际足联秘书长[[瓦尔克·杰罗姆|瓦尔克·杰罗姆]]则为工程进度辩护，指出“所有项目从一开始就未准备就绪，政府计划中的某些工程明显超出了世界杯范围<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10674187/World-Cup-2014-There-are-100-days-to-the-start-of-the-big-show-will-Brazil-be-ready.html|title=There are 100 days to the start of the big show – will Brazil be ready?|date=4 March 2014|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2017-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121140837/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10674187/World-Cup-2014-There-are-100-days-to-the-start-of-the-big-show-will-Brazil-be-ready.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。国际足联承诺赛后至少将花费2000万美元用于“遗产项目”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2013/m=12/news=fifa-launches-2014-fifa-world-cup-legacy-trust-2239771.html|title=FIFA launches 2014 FIFA World Cup Legacy Trust|date=5 December 2013|publisher=FIFA|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702112042/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2013/m=12/news=fifa-launches-2014-fifa-world-cup-legacy-trust-2239771.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

原定计划未能全部完成，成为一些巴西人批评政府对赛事的投资和项目处理的原因。Datafolha在赛前两个月开展的民意调查中，仅有48%的巴西受访者对赛事表示支持，较2008年的79%大幅下降<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/04/08/us-worldcup-brazil-idUSBREA3715H20140408|title=Less than half of Brazilians favor hosting World Cup, poll shows|publisher=Reuters|date=8 April 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709131520/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/04/08/us-worldcup-brazil-idUSBREA3715H20140408|dead-url=no}}</ref>。55%受访者相信赛事对巴西人弊大于利<ref name="USAToday">{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/soccer/worldcup/2014/05/27/world-cup-brazil-protests-rio-de-janeiro/9616607/|title=There are 100 days to the start of the big show – will Brazil be ready?|date=27 May 2014|publisher=USA Today|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140731133539/http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/soccer/worldcup/2014/05/27/world-cup-brazil-protests-rio-de-janeiro/9616607/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国际足联主席布拉特承认“因为许诺的东西太多，巴西民众都有点不满<ref name="USAToday"/>”。

现从政的前巴西足球运动员[[罗马里奥|罗马里奥]]批评国家对准备工作的处理，但表示“国际足联的要求过分”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1663701-the-social-cost-of-brazil-hosting-world-cup-2014|title=The social cost of Brazil hosting World Cup 2014|publisher=Bleacher Report|date=6 June 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111150740/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1663701-the-social-cost-of-brazil-hosting-world-cup-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一位前球员[[罗纳尔多|罗纳尔多]]表示，国家的基础设施和一系列所承诺投资未兑现——仅兑现了30%让自己“尴尬”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27632572|title=Fifa concern about three Brazil stadiums|date=30 May 2014|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114061702/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27632572|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

