== 安保措施 ==
巴西政府承诺9亿美元的投资用于安全部队，使得赛事成为“有史以来最受保护的体育盛事之一”<ref name="CNN">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/12/05/sport/football/brazil-world-cup-security-football/|title=Brazil boosts World Cup security budget as crime rises|publisher=CNN|date=5 December 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2018-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181212103345/https://edition.cnn.com/2012/12/05/sport/football/brazil-world-cup-security-football/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。每50人出席赛事和每80人在公众场合观看赛事就配备一名警察<ref name="CNN"/>。

安全方面的投资包括[[人脸识别|人脸识别]]系统和无人操作机器人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.brazilmycountry.com/brazil-going-to-use-robots-to-help-with-2014-world-cup-security/ |title=Brazil going to use robots to help with 2014 World Cup security |publisher=Brazil My Country |date=15 May 2013 |accessdate=15 May 2013 |archive-date=2017-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116185721/http://www.brazilmycountry.com/brazil-going-to-use-robots-to-help-with-2014-world-cup-security/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，旨在获得有关潜在恐怖分子、闹事者和足球流氓情报的安全计划亦被制定<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.copa2014.gov.br/noticia/integration-keyword-strategic-security-plan?language=en|title=Integration is the keyword in the Strategic Security Plan|publisher=World Cup Portal|date=14 September 2009|access-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629062207/http://www.copa2014.gov.br/noticia/integration-keyword-strategic-security-plan?language=en|archive-date=2014-06-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。共15万公安专业人士和军人参与安保工作，另有两万名私人保安协助<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sportsfan.com.au/brazils-massive-world-cup-security-force/tabid/91/newsid/123661/default.aspx |title=Brazil's massive World Cup security forces |publisher=Sportsfan.com.au |accessdate=12 May 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227021808/http://www.sportsfan.com.au/brazils-massive-world-cup-security-force/tabid/91/newsid/123661/default.aspx |archivedate=2014年2月27日 }}</ref>。

鉴于2013年洲际国家杯期间场外发生的[[2013年巴西抗议运动|大规模抗议]]，赛事的安全考虑已提升<ref>{{cite web|title=Brazil Maracana stadium protest ends in clashes|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-22930402|publisher=BBC News|date=16 June 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2019-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220012020/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-22930402|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Brazil unrest: 'Million' join protests in 100 cities|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-22992410|publisher=BBC News|date=21 June 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2019-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530163057/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-22992410|dead-url=no}}</ref>。示威者主要不满政府给社会服务大量投钱<ref>{{cite web|title=Brazil's protests raise fears for World Cup as a million take to the streets|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/jun/21/brazil-protests-football-world-cup|work=The Guardian|date=21 June 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610165350/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/jun/21/brazil-protests-football-world-cup|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=World Cup only benefits outsiders, say Brazil protesters|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/06/18/world/americas/brazil-protests-montague/index.html|publisher=CNN|date=19 June 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2017-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116184852/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/06/18/world/americas/brazil-protests-montague/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=In the favelas on the frontline of protest, Brazilians ask: who is this World Cup for?|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/jun/22/brazil-favelas-frontline-world-cup|work=The Guardian|date=22 June 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140830042509/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/jun/22/brazil-favelas-frontline-world-cup|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 观赛指引 ==
國際足協（FIFA）列出的「球場守則」非常嚴謹，除了禁攜煙火外，大面積的[[國旗|國旗]]和[[橫額|橫額]]也不得進場，最令人驚訝的是，[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]、[[手提電腦|手提電腦]]等也不准攜帶，守則列明指[[錄影機|錄影機]]和任何可拍錄[[聲音|聲音]]和[[影像|影像]]的設備，或可透過網絡等媒介傳輸結果的設備均不得攜帶入場，但至於[[智能手機|智能手機]]則網開一面，又允許球迷用相機捕捉精采時刻，但只可用作私人用途，而且只能帶一組電池。

此外守則指示球迷不得外帶[[食物|食物]]進場，最多只能在場內購買，而橫額和國旗最多2米長、1.5米寬，而易燃的旗幟、噴霧罐、粉末、傘以及任何發出巨大聲浪的器具亦不准攜帶。隨身物品的長度、寬度和深度均有限制，一律不得超過25厘米，並特別呼籲球迷避免「拖篋」或帶大背包進場。

== 技术投入 ==
2013年2月，国际足联宣布，将在巴西世界杯上启用门线技术，减少误判事件发生。

2013年12月，国际足联主席布拉特表示，在本届世界杯上，将采用限定任意球人墙距离的喷雾技术。裁判测距后，用一种特制的泡沫喷雾剂划定警戒线，可以有效防止球员越界，同时裁判也会用喷雾划定罚任意球时球应放的位置，喷雾的痕迹可在一分钟之内消失。

